Global Webtoon Self-Publishing Platform Market Insights
Webtoon Self-Publishing Platform Market size was valued at USD 1.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 5 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 15% from 2024 to 2030.

Webtoon Self-Publishing Platform Market Overview
The global Webtoon self-publishing platform market was valued at approximately $4.21 billion in 2023 and is projected to reach around $5.60 billion by 2030, growing at a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 5.4% during the forecast period. This growth is driven by the increasing popularity of digital comics and the rise of independent content creation. Platforms like LINE Webtoon, Tapas, and Lezhin Comics have empowered creators to publish their work directly to a global audience, bypassing traditional publishing barriers. The demand for diverse and niche content has attracted more creators, transforming webtoon creation into a viable career path. Monetization options, such as ad revenue sharing, crowdfunding, and premium subscriptions, have further fueled this growth. As the market matures, platforms are investing in globalization efforts, including translation services, to expand reach across international markets. This democratization of content creation has also led to the discovery of new talent, with many webtoon creators securing partnership deals or seeing their work adapted into other media formats, such as TV shows and films. Source

